The tomatoes are full grown and bright red. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The jalapeño peppers are 2–3 inches (5.1–7.6 cm) in length and somewhere between a dark green and a bright red (bright red spots mean the pepper is ripening further, which is perfectly ok.){"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/90/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/90/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The shoots on the onions and garlic are beginning to turn yellow and dry out. Note: This is not required - both can be harvested while shoots are still green and fresh-looking. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d0/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d0/Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Grow-Salsa-Ingredients-in-a-Drawer-Step-32Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
